{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-02721/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-02721"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:27:21"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, pan"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["dirty single"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman speaks to another woman."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-02721","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-02721"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/canvas/1/2f0c1d0b-5ed7-49fa-b7d4-c747c921287f","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:20:53.421Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Cyril wears almost the exact shade of blue that Reynolds had dismissed for Alma’s dress as “too serious.” This speaks to the difference in their roles in his life. While Cyril is his partner and can take part in his business and other serious matters, Alma is meant to remain on the outside.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:785.0437121721586,550.9751176866174,409.3073301950237,436.4223268325487"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/canvas/1/dfc064a7-425c-4cbd-bf6e-cef5d1990e80","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:21:16.555Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds and Cyril share a strong olfactory sense. The former <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW180430128 BCX4\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-15153.html\"><u>detects an air of “quiet death”</u></a> in his house, while the latter smells Alma and what she had for dinner on her first date with Reynolds. The sour smell of lemons is thus replaced by something even more sinister over the course of the film.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02721/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:915.4539340954942,393.4498991257566,135.57498318762612,114.91593813046399"}}}]}]}]}